00:28:24.299 --> 00:28:27.979
And David was a man that knew God intimately.

00:28:30.459 --> 00:28:32.019
And he says in the Lord put I my trust.

00:28:32.019 --> 00:28:32.859
Why?

00:28:32.859 --> 00:28:34.779
Because he knew the name of God.

00:28:35.659 --> 00:28:38.819
I'll finish with this verse in Psalm 148.

00:28:38.819 --> 00:28:42.059
We talk about the impact of knowing God's names.

00:28:42.059 --> 00:28:44.059
Listen, this evening when we truly know who he is,

00:28:44.059 --> 00:28:45.579
when we know his names,

00:28:46.859 --> 00:28:48.619
we know him in that intimate way,

00:28:48.619 --> 00:28:49.819
we're gonna trust him.

00:28:50.819 --> 00:28:52.939
In Psalm 148, in verse 13,

00:28:54.859 --> 00:28:55.699
the Bible says,

00:28:55.699 --> 00:28:58.299
let them praise the name of the Lord.

00:28:58.299 --> 00:29:01.179
For his name alone is excellent.

00:29:01.179 --> 00:29:06.179
His glory is above the earth and heaven.

00:29:09.259 --> 00:29:11.339
Let them praise the name of the Lord.

00:29:11.339 --> 00:29:16.339
For his name alone is excellent.

00:29:16.739 --> 00:29:18.739
And I hope this evening

00:29:18.739 --> 00:29:21.699
that you already know some of the names of God.

00:29:22.939 --> 00:29:24.699
But I hope that over the next several months

00:29:24.699 --> 00:29:28.499
as we study through these names of God,

00:29:28.499 --> 00:29:31.099
that we will grow spiritually.

00:29:31.099 --> 00:29:34.099
That we will learn various aspects

00:29:34.099 --> 00:29:37.659
of who our God is to us personally

00:29:37.659 --> 00:29:39.939
and what he's able to do for us.

00:29:39.939 --> 00:29:41.579
And that it would strengthen our faith

00:29:41.579 --> 00:29:45.059
and it would cause us to trust him.

00:29:45.499 --> 00:29:48.099
To trust him as we should.

00:29:49.259 --> 00:29:51.899
Here in Psalm 91, where we started this evening,

00:29:51.899 --> 00:29:56.899
it says, because he hath known my name.

00:29:57.939 --> 00:30:00.019
Because he hath known my name.

00:30:00.019 --> 00:30:06.659
desire that we would know the name of the Lord, and I'll make it plural, the names of

00:30:06.659 --> 00:30:08.899
the Lord, because there are so many of them.

00:30:08.899 --> 00:30:09.899
Let's pray together.

00:30:09.899 --> 00:30:11.139
Father, we do love you.

00:30:11.139 --> 00:30:12.259
Thank you for loving us.

00:30:12.259 --> 00:30:14.099
Thank you for your grace.

00:30:14.099 --> 00:30:16.779
Thank you for your word tonight and the truth that's revealed.

00:30:16.779 --> 00:30:22.579
I pray, God, that you'd help us to know your names, Lord, that we would be excited about

00:30:22.579 --> 00:30:23.579
this study.

00:30:23.579 --> 00:30:25.899
I'm excited about what you have in store for us.

00:30:25.899 --> 00:30:29.699
God, I pray that you'd strengthen us, that you'd help us to grow spiritually, that you'd

00:30:29.699 --> 00:30:34.219
help us to trust you more, because we know your name.

00:30:34.219 --> 00:30:35.579
Thank you for the privilege of prayer.

00:30:35.579 --> 00:30:36.939
We thank you that you hear and answer.

00:30:36.939 --> 00:30:39.219
We pray that you'd work, move, as only you can.

00:30:39.219 --> 00:30:41.659
For it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

